---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---

<BaseLayout title="Mental Wellbeing Case Study" description="Designing a culturally sensitive mental health ecosystem.">
  <article class="prose max-w-none">
    <div class="mb-12">
      <a
        href="/projects"
        class="no-underline text-zinc-400 hover:text-white text-sm font-bold flex items-center gap-2 mb-8 transition-colors"
      >
        <span class="i-carbon-arrow-left"></span> Back to Projects
      </a>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mb-6">
        <span
          class="bg-emerald-900/40 text-emerald-200 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-xs font-mono border border-emerald-800/50"
        >
          <span class="i-carbon-user-speaker mr-1 align-middle"></span> 1st Author (IEEE)
        </span>
        <span
          class="bg-purple-900/40 text-purple-200 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-xs font-mono border border-purple-800/50"
        >
          <span class="i-carbon-mobile mr-1 align-middle"></span> iOS / Android
        </span>
        <span class="bg-blue-900/40 text-blue-200 px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-xs font-mono border border-blue-800/50">
          <span class="i-carbon-stem-leaf-plot mr-1 align-middle"></span> Research
        </span>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold m-0 text-white leading-tight mb-6">
        Designing a culturally sensitive mental wellbeing digital solution.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-zinc-400 m-0 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
        Bridging the gap between academic stress and help-seeking behavior for international students through <span
          class="text-emerald-400">Participatory Design</span
        > and <span class="text-purple-400">Generative AI</span>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div
      class="w-full aspect-video bg-zinc-900/30 rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 flex flex-col items-center justify-center mb-16 overflow-hidden relative group"
    >
      <img
        src="/Portfolio.png"
        alt="Mental Wellbeing App UI Mockups"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105"
      />
    </div>

    <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mb-20 border-b border-zinc-800 pb-12">
      <div class="col-span-1">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">My Role</h3>
        <p class="text-white m-0">Lead UX Researcher & Product Designer</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-1">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Timeline</h3>
        <p class="text-white m-0">Aug 2024 - Present</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-1">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Tools</h3>
        <p class="text-white m-0">Figma, React Native, Python (Pandas)</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-1">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Team</h3>
        <p class="text-white m-0">Advisor: Dr. Charlotte Tang</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-24">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
        <span class="i-carbon-microscope text-2xl text-emerald-400"></span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white m-0">The Research Gap</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <p class="text-zinc-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
            International students are a high-risk group for acculturative stress, yet they are the least likely to use
            university health services due to <strong>cultural stigma</strong> and <strong>privacy concerns</strong>.
          </p>
          <div class="p-6 bg-zinc-900/50 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-emerald-500">
            <p class="italic text-zinc-400 m-0">
              "I feel guilty spending money on therapy when my parents are sacrificing so much for my tuition."
            </p>
            <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 mt-2 font-mono">— Participant #04, Graduate Student</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4">
          <div
            class="p-6 bg-zinc-900/30 rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 flex items-center justify-between group hover:border-emerald-500/50 transition-colors"
          >
            <div>
              <span class="block text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-1">93.8%</span>
              <span class="text-xs font-bold text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Academic Pressure</span>
            </div>
            <span class="i-carbon-education text-4xl text-zinc-700 group-hover:text-emerald-500/50 transition-colors"
            ></span>
          </div>
          <div
            class="p-6 bg-zinc-900/30 rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 flex items-center justify-between group hover:border-emerald-500/50 transition-colors"
          >
            <div>
              <span class="block text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-1">93.2%</span>
              <span class="text-xs font-bold text-zinc-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Financial Stress</span>
            </div>
            <span class="i-carbon-currency text-4xl text-zinc-700 group-hover:text-emerald-500/50 transition-colors"
            ></span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full mt-12 max-w-full overflow-hidden">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <span class="i-carbon-presentation-file text-2xl text-blue-400"></span>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white m-0">Theoretical Framework</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-8 max-w-3xl">
          Our digital solution is grounded in Acculturative Stress Theory. This framework allowed us to map both
          extrinsic stressors (financial, academic) and intrinsic stressors directly to actionable UX features.
        </p>
        <div
          class="relative w-full aspect-video bg-zinc-900/50 rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 flex items-center justify-center p-2 md:p-4 overflow-hidden group"
        >
          <img
            src="/accul.png"
            alt="Acculturative Stress Theory Framework from IEEE Presentation"
            class="max-w-full max-h-full object-contain transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-24">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
        <span class="i-carbon-group text-2xl text-purple-400"></span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white m-0">Participatory Design</h2>
      </div>

      <p class="text-zinc-300 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-3xl">
        We didn't just design <em>for</em> students; we designed <em>with</em> them. Through sticky-note sessions and voting
        rounds, a critical insight emerged that pivoted the entire product direction.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-12">
        <div class="p-8 bg-zinc-900/30 rounded-xl border border-zinc-800">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">The Pivot: "The Wellness Wallet"</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-400 m-0">
            Participants rejected the idea of a "Clinical App." They wanted a <strong>"Stealth UI"</strong>—an interface
            that looks like a productivity or finance tool. This disguises mental health tracking, allowing them to use
            the app in public without fear of judgment.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl border border-zinc-700 flex items-center justify-center min-h-[200px]">
          <img
            src="/pd.jpeg"
            alt="Mental Wellbeing App UI Mockups"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105"
            <
            div
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <section class="mb-24">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
          <span class="i-carbon-mobile text-2xl text-blue-400"></span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white m-0">The Solution</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-16 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_300px] gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">AI Peer Support (Gemini)</h3>
            <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-6">
              Leveraging LLMs to provide low-barrier, conversational support. The AI is finetuned to act as an
              "experienced peer" rather than a doctor, reducing the intimidation factor of seeking help.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-zinc-300 text-sm">
                <span class="i-carbon-checkmark-filled text-blue-500 mt-1"></span>
                Culturally aware responses (e.g., understanding filial piety).
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-zinc-300 text-sm">
                <span class="i-carbon-checkmark-filled text-blue-500 mt-1"></span>
                24/7 availability for late-night anxiety spikes.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div
            class="h-[500px] bg-zinc-900 rounded-3xl border border-zinc-700 shadow-2xl shadow-black flex items-center justify-center"
          >
            <img
              src="/aichat.png"
              alt="Mental Wellbeing App UI Mockups"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105"
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-16 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[300px_1fr] gap-12 items-center">
          <div
            class="h-[500px] bg-zinc-900 rounded-3xl border border-zinc-700 shadow-2xl shadow-black flex items-center justify-center order-2 md:order-1"
          >
            <img
              src="/rewards.png"
              alt="Mental Wellbeing App UI Mockups"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-3">The Prestige System</h3>
            <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-6">
              Directly addressing the 93.2% financial stress metric. Students earn "Prestige Points" for mindfulness
              streaks, which can be redeemed for small campus dining credits—turning self-care into a tangible financial
              benefit.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="w-full mt-12">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-6">User Flowchart</h3>
          <div
            class="w-full h-[800px] md:h-[1000px] bg-zinc-900/50 rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 flex items-center justify-center p-4 md:p-8 overflow-hidden group"
          >
            <img
              src="/flowchart.png"
              alt="Mental Wellbeing App User Flowchart"
              class="w-full h-full object-contain transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </section>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 border-t border-zinc-800 pt-12">
      <a
        href="https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/11328367"
        target="_blank"
        class="flex-1 text-center px-6 py-4 bg-zinc-900 hover:bg-zinc-700 text-zinc-900 font-bold rounded-xl transition-colors no-underline"
      >
        Read IEEE Paper
        <span class="i-carbon-launch ml-2 text-zinc-500"></span>
      </a>
      <a
        href="#"
        class="flex-1 text-center px-6 py-4 bg-zinc-900 hover:bg-zinc-800 text-white font-bold rounded-xl border border-zinc-700 transition-colors no-underline"
      >
        View GitHub Repo
        <span class="i-carbon-logo-github ml-2"></span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
